  "prompt": "How people make money by answering questions in Qoura?",
  "response": "On Quora (not Qoura), people can potentially earn money through the Quora Partner Program (QPP) in several ways:\n\n1. Partner Program\n- Answer questions frequently and high-quality\n- Get paid based on question views and engagement\n- Invitation-only program\n- Earnings depend on traffic and question quality\n\n2. Monetization methods\n- Ad revenue sharing\n- Earn money per view of their answers\n- More views = more potential earnings\n- Quality and relevance of answers matter\n\n3. Requirements\n- Must be active on platform\n- Consistent high-quality content\n- Engaging and informative answers\n- Build reputation and followers\n\n4. Additional opportunities\n- Become a Quora Top Writer\n- Create sponsored content\n- Attract freelance/consulting opportunities\n- Build professional network\n\n5. Tips to increase earnings\n- Write comprehensive answers\n- Use proper formatting\n- Include credible sources\n- Answer trending/popular questions\n- Be consistent in posting\n\n6. Limitations\n- Not guaranteed income\n- Earnings can be unpredictable\n- Not everyone gets invited to Partner Program\n- Requires significant time investment\n\nRemember, success on Quora depends on providing valuable, original content that helps readers.",
